# Sidebar Collapsed View Shortcuts

Add circular shortcut buttons to the sidebar when it is in its collapsed state, allowing users to switch categories without expanding the sidebar.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The sidebar width in collapsed mode is 60px. The circular buttons will be centered in this space.

## Proposed Changes

### GeminiLauncher

- [MODIFY] [ResourcesPage.xaml](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/ResourcesPage.xaml)
- Restructure the root `Grid` to ensure `DashboardLayer` and overlays are direct siblings.
- Ensure overlays have `Grid.Column="0" Grid.ColumnSpan="2"` (if columns exist at root) or simply no column restrictions.
- Fix the `DashboardLayer` fade-out trigger to ensure the sidebar also disappears when `IsFullPageView` is true.
- Move the `Import Progress Overlay` to the same root level.

